*libnm-qt-0.9.8.0 (21 Nov 2013)

  21 Nov 2013; Johannes Huber <johu@gentoo.org> +libnm-qt-0.9.8.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  16 Oct 2013; Johannes Huber <johu@gentoo.org>
  +files/libnm-qt-0.9.0.1-libmm-optional.patch, libnm-qt-0.9.0.1.ebuild:
  Backport upstream patch spotted by Bartosz Brachaczek
  <b.brachaczek@gmail.com>. Fixes build with USE="-modemmanager" and net-libs
  /libmm-qt not installed, bug #488238.

*libnm-qt-0.9.0.1 (15 Oct 2013)

  15 Oct 2013; Johannes Huber <johu@gentoo.org> +libnm-qt-0.9.0.1.ebuild,
  +files/libnm-qt-0.9.0.1-tests-optional.patch, +metadata.xml:
  New package. Import from kde overlay, Qt networkmanager abstraction library.
  Will be required for kde-misc/plasma-nm.
